ABOUT

I graduated with a bachelor's degree and college diploma in Justice Studies and Police Foundations in 2019, and will be graduating with a diploma in Software Engineering Technican in spring of 2022.

I have over 7 years of diverse work place experience, ranging from a court clerk assistant to a data network analyst. In my free time, I fuel my creative side by painting, sketching, and prowling the neighborhood for stray cats.
